      "content": "Interesting. You mentioned Candidate B's delivery is \"completely unsuitable\" for representing a company, but if you look at the actual content of their answers, they are saying the exact same things as Candidate A. Don't you think the actual substance of their problem-solving is just as strong? Why does the specific way they phrase things make them a bad hire in your view?",
